{"data":[{"name":"77:1","price":" Yemin olsun, birbiri ardınca gönderilenlere;","arabic":"وَٱلۡمُرۡسَلَٰتِ عُرۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5623,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:2","price":" Şiddetle esip savrulanlara;","arabic":"فَٱلۡعَٰصِفَٰتِ عَصۡفٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5624,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:3","price":" Yaydıkça yayanlara;","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِرَٰتِ نَشۡرٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5625,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:4","price":" Ayırdıkça ayıranlara;","arabic":"فَٱلۡفَٰرِقَٰتِ فَرۡقٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5626,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:5","price":"Zikri ulaştıranlara;","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُلۡقِيَٰتِ ذِكۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5627,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:6","price":" Özür veya korkutmak için,","arabic":"عُذۡرًا أَوۡ نُذۡرًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5628,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:7","price":" Size vadedilen elbette gerçekleşecektir.","arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5629,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:8","price":" Yıldızların ışığı söndüğü zaman; ","arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5630,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:9","price":" Gök yarıldığı;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5631,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:10","price":" Dağlar un ufak savrulduğu zaman; ","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ نُسِفَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5632,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:11","price":" Rasûller toplandığı zaman;","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5633,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:12","price":"Bu hangi güne ertelenmiş? ","arabic":"لِأَيِّ يَوۡمٍ أُجِّلَتۡ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5634,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:13","price":" Ayırma gününe. ","arabic":"لِيَوۡمِ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5635,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:14","price":" Hüküm gününün ne olduğunu ne bilirsin?","arabic":"وَمَآ أَدۡرَىٰكَ مَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5636,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:15","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5637,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:16","price":" Evvelkileri helak etmedik mi? ","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نُهۡلِكِ ٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5638,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:17","price":" Sonra arkadakileri de onların ardına takacağız.","arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتۡبِعُهُمُ ٱلۡأٓخِرِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5639,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:18","price":" İşte suçlulara böyle yaparız!","arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفۡعَلُ بِٱلۡمُجۡرِمِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5640,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:19","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5641,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:20","price":" Sizi basit bir sudan yaratmadık mı? ","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَخۡلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٖ مَّهِينٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5642,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:21","price":" Ve suyu sağlam bir yere yerleştirmedik mi?","arabic":"فَجَعَلۡنَٰهُ فِي قَرَارٖ مَّكِينٍ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5643,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:22","price":" Belli bir süreye kadar ","arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٖ مَّعۡلُومٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5644,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:23","price":" Buna gücümüz yetti. Ne güzel güç yetirenleriz","arabic":"فَقَدَرۡنَا فَنِعۡمَ ٱلۡقَٰدِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5645,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:24","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5646,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:25","price":" Yeryüzünü toplanma yeri kılmadık mı?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ كِفَاتًا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5647,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:26","price":" Dirilere ve ölülere.","arabic":"أَحۡيَآءٗ وَأَمۡوَٰتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5648,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:27","price":" Orada yüksek dağlar yaratıp size tatlı su içirmedik mi? ","arabic":"وَجَعَلۡنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِيَ شَٰمِخَٰتٖ وَأَسۡقَيۡنَٰكُم مَّآءٗ فُرَاتٗا","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5649,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:28","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5650,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:29","price":" Haydi yalanladığınıza yürüyün. ","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5651,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:30","price":" Yürüyün üç kollu (ateşin) gölgesine!","arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓاْ إِلَىٰ ظِلّٖ ذِي ثَلَٰثِ شُعَبٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5652,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:31","price":" Gölgelendirmez, alevden de korumaz. ","arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٖ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5653,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:32","price":"O, köşk gibi kocaman kıvılcım saçar.","arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرۡمِي بِشَرَرٖ كَٱلۡقَصۡرِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5654,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:33","price":"Her bir kıvılcım, sanki birer sarı deve gibidir.","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَٰلَتٞ صُفۡرٞ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5655,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:34","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5656,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:35","price":" Bu, onların konuşamayacakları bir gündür ","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5657,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:36","price":" Özür dilemeleri için onlara izin verilmez","arabic":"وَلَا يُؤۡذَنُ لَهُمۡ فَيَعۡتَذِرُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5658,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:37","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5659,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:38","price":" Bu, ayırma günüdür Sizi ve evvelkileri bir araya toplarız ","arabic":"هَٰذَا يَوۡمُ ٱلۡفَصۡلِۖ جَمَعۡنَٰكُمۡ وَٱلۡأَوَّلِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5660,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:39","price":" Eğer bana karşı bir tuzağınız varsa, onu hemen kurun! ","arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمۡ كَيۡدٞ فَكِيدُونِ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5661,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:40","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5662,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:41","price":" Allah’tan sakınanlar ise gölgeler içinde ve pınar başlarındadır.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡمُتَّقِينَ فِي ظِلَٰلٖ وَعُيُونٖ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5663,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:42","price":" Arzu ettikleri meyveler…","arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشۡتَهُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5664,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:43","price":" Yaptıklarınıza karşılık afiyetle yiyin, için!","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَٱشۡرَبُواْ هَنِيٓـَٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمۡ تَعۡمَلُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5665,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:44","price":" Biz, iyilik yapanları işte böyle ödüllendiririz.","arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجۡزِي ٱلۡمُحۡسِنِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5666,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:45","price":" Yalanlayanların o gün vay haline!","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5667,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:46","price":" Yiyin ve azıcık faydalanın, nasılsa siz suçlusunuz!","arabic":"كُلُواْ وَتَمَتَّعُواْ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجۡرِمُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5668,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:47","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5669,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:48","price":"Onlara, “Rükû edin!” denildiği zaman, rükû etmezlerdi.","arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرۡكَعُواْ لَا يَرۡكَعُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5670,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:49","price":" Vay haline o gün, yalanlayanların! ","arabic":"وَيۡلٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لِّلۡمُكَذِّبِينَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5671,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"},{"name":"77:50","price":"Onlar artık bundan (Kur'an'dan) sonra hangi söze iman edecekler?","arabic":"فَبِأَيِّ حَدِيثِۭ بَعۡدَهُۥ يُؤۡمِنُونَ","category":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat"],"ayahNumber":5672,"juzNumber":29,"footnotes":null,"lang":"tr"}],"chapter":["77 (Al-Mursalat)","Al-Mursalat","Surah Al-Mursalat","Chapter Al-Mursalat","Mursalat","Surah Mursalat","Chapter Mursalat","Al Mursalat","Surah Al Mursalat","Chapter Al Mursalat","Surah 77","Chapter 77","The Emissaries","المرسلات"]}